{
  "design_notes": "Designed an Easy chart perfectly tailored for dance pad gameplay. Kept density well below 3.0 NPS overall (mostly half notes, peaking briefly into quarter notes) to ensure readability and legibility for beginner to casual players. Holds are placed on clear vocal/synth sustain notes, taking up roughly 10% of total notes. Density maps closely to the energy curve of the music, escalating into the drops and easing up during transitions and breakdown. Completely crossover and jack-free, using intuitive movement directions and only 0.5 beat grid alignments.",
